#: ../../../release_details/9.5/openfoam-restart-files.md:1
msgid "OpenFOAM reader: allow `_0` files"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/openfoam-restart-files.md:3
msgid ""
"The OpenFOAM file reader in VTK now provides an option to load file names "
"which ends with `_0`. The loading was disabled because OpenFOAM restart "
"files usually ends with `_0`, but it prevented loading of actual result "
"files with the same naming schema."
msgstr ""
